unID=100 CALL "fa_gen_basecabinet" PARAMETERS a=a, b=b, zzyzx=zzyzx, gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, dob_face=dob_face, count_th=count_th, front_cab=front_cab, rear_cab=rear_cab, left_cab=left_cab, right_cab=right_cab, toe_h=toe_h, side_vis_m=side_vis_m+1, sink=0, shelf_num=shelf_num, gs_ShelfMat=gs_ShelfMat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow, toe_mat=toe_mat, gs_cabinet_mat=gs_cabinet_mat, drawer_h=temp_drawer_h, toe_d = toe_d,gs_toe_type_m=gs_toe_type_m,fr_th1=fr_th1, basecab_unID=unID, returned_parameters unID

addx a - right_cab + left_cab mulx -1
next i del (i-1)*2

IF left_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD left_cab,door_w+fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ -90 GOSUB "endPanels2" DEL 2 ENDIF
IF right_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD a-right_cab,fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ 90 GOSUB "endPanels2" DEL 2 ENDIF

Symbol.Script_VL:
VALUES "A" range (0, ) VALUES "B" range (0, )
values "ApplType" st_ApplType values "ApplType_m" APPLTYPE_MIC_OVEN, APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN, APPLTYPE_COMB_OVEN, APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN, APPLTYPE_NONE
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ApplType" then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_MIC_OVEN if ApplType = st_ApplType[2] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN if ApplType = st_ApplType[3] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_COMB_OVEN if ApplType = st_ApplType[4] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN if ApplType = st_ApplType[5] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_NONE parameters ApplType_m = ApplType_m else ApplType = st_ApplType[1] if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN then ApplType = st_ApplType[2] if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_COMB_OVEN then ApplType = st_ApplType[3] if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN then ApplType = st_ApplType[4] if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_NONE then ApplType = st_ApplType[5] parameters ApplType = ApplType endif
values "OvenDoorStyle" st_OvenDoorStyles values "ApplStyle_m" APPLSTYLE_1, APPLSTYLE_2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "OvenDoorStyle" then ApplStyle_m = APPLSTYLE_1 if OvenDoorStyle = st_OvenDoorStyles[2] then ApplStyle_m = 2 parameters ApplStyle_m = ApplStyle_m else OvenDoorStyle = st_OvenDoorStyles[1] if ApplStyle_m = APPLSTYLE_2 then OvenDoorStyle = st_OvenDoorStyles[2] parameters OvenDoorStyle = OvenDoorStyle endif
values "door_ang" range [0,180]
! --- Minimal Space --- values "MSSide" range (-a/2,] values "MSSide2" range (-a/2,] IF UpCabinet=1 THEN values "low_door_h" range [toe_h+0.1,ZZYZX-ApplHeight-0.1] values "ApplHeight" range [toe_h+0.1,ZZYZX-low_door_h-0.1] ELSE values "ApplHeight" range [0.1,ZZYZX-toe_h-0.1] ENDIF
! --- Mic-Oven Doors ---
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="ApplType_m" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="ApplType" then
IF ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_MIC_OVEN THEN ApplHeight = 0.4 PARAMETERS ApplHeight = ApplHeight ENDIF
IF ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN THEN ApplHeight = 0.5 PARAMETERS ApplHeight = ApplHeight ENDIF
IF ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_COMB_OVEN THEN ApplHeight = 0.8 PARAMETERS ApplHeight = ApplHeight ENDIF
IF ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN THEN ApplHeight = 0.9 PARAMETERS ApplHeight = ApplHeight ENDIF
ENDIF
IF UpCabinet=1 THEN up_door_h = zzyzx-low_door_h-ApplHeight PARAMETERS up_door_h = up_door_h LOCK "up_door_h" ELSE low_door_h = zzyzx-ApplHeight PARAMETERS low_door_h = low_door_h LOCK "up_door_h","low_door_h" ENDIF
! --- LOCK PARAMETERS ---
